Package: opera
Type: Package
Title: Online Prediction by Expert Aggregation
Version: 1.2.0
Author: Pierre Gaillard [cre, aut],
  Yannig Goude [aut],
  Laurent Plagne [ctb],
  Thibaut Dubois [ctb],
